summary:
I am a highly competent livestock technocrat well equipped with a variety of working skills ranging from managerial to field expertise with government and humanitarian entities; CBOs, CSOs, N/INGOs and government agencies since 2008.

Always ready to work under hard and difficult environments and situations; ready to work extra time towards achievment of project/program's goal and objectives; highly flexible and ready to agree and disagree at the interest of the program/organization.

And above al,l committed, reliable and trustworthy
